# Privacy Policy for PSA Hot Lunch

# Last Updated: 2/13/24

Welcome to PSA Hot Lunch, your go-to app for the daily school lunch menu. Our mission is to make your lunch decisions easier by providing a single, curated lunch option directly from our GitHub repository. This Privacy Policy is designed to inform you about our commitment to not collecting personal data and to ensure a transparent understanding of our notification feature.

## 1. Information We Do Not Collect

We prioritize your privacy. Our app is built to operate without collecting any personal information from you. We do not require user registration, and we do not track, store, or process any personal data such as names, email addresses, or location information.

## 2. Lunch menu

Our app provides a single lunch suggestion daily, specifically designed for PSA. This suggestion is retrieved from a publicly available repository on GitHub, managed by our team, ensuring that you receive a quality lunch option without compromising your privacy.

## 3. Notifications for Lunch Orders

To enhance your experience, PSA Hot Lunch includes a feature to send notifications reminding you to place your lunch order. We understand the importance of choice, which is why this notification feature can be easily turned off within the app settings. This ensures that you have control over the reminders you receive.

## 4. GitHub's Privacy Practices

While our app does not collect personal information, we rely on GitHub for hosting the lunch menu. We recommend reviewing GitHub's Privacy Policy to understand their data handling practices, as our service's functionality involves interacting with GitHub's platform.

## 5. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update or change our Privacy Policy at any time. Any modifications will be effective immediately upon posting the updated policy on this page. We encourage you to periodically review this policy to stay informed of any changes.

## 6. Contact Us

Should you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or the app's features, please don't hesitate to reach out to us by email: michael555hall@gmail.com

# Conclusion

Our dedication at PSA Hot Lunch is to offer a convenient and straightforward lunch menu for your school meals while upholding the highest standards of privacy. We are committed to ensuring that your experience is both enjoyable and secure, with full control over the notifications you receive.
